lead_paragraph: In another drama-filled, rainy extra-inning game, the Los Angeles Dodgers got right back into their first series with the San Francisco Giants as these clubs seek supremacy in the NL West come September — and ace Clayton Kershaw didn't even factor into the outcome this time.

headline.print_headline: Bumgarner Homers Off Kershaw Again, but Dodgers Win in 10th
